sequenceDiagram
    participant U as 用户
    participant L1 as L1 inbox 合约
    participant S as L2 Sequencer
    participant L2 as L2 状态

    U->>L1: 把交易发到 L1 inbox
    L1->>S: sequencer 必须在 N 区块内打包
    alt sequencer 不打包
        L1->>L2: 强制执行（force-included）
        Note over L2: 抗审查兜底
    else sequencer 正常打包
        S->>L2: 正常处理
    end